about.description: Python bindings to the Zenhub API
about.summary: Python bindings to the Zenhub API

name: pyzenhub
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyzenhub" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}
{% set hash = "b64fc47a262132011c6d0d03e03344eed111862a62350c1f6e36c60050824430" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ hash }}
  
build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - requests

test:
  imports:
    - zenhub

about:
  home: https://github.com/goanpeca/pyzenhub
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Python bindings to the Zenhub API'
  description: |
    Python bindings to the Zenhub API
  doc_url: https://github.com/goanpeca/pyzenhub
  dev_url: https://github.com/goanpeca/pyzenhub

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - goanpeca
